snippet.title: Party Versus 🥔💥 Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Game night can take place anywhere thanks to Party Versus! 2-4 players can experience the next level of social gaming with this mixed-reality party game with dozens of mini-games exclusively for the Meta Quest 3 and Quest 3S.

Developed by Schell Games, Party Versus lets you play with friends and family across the world - in your own home!

Play dozens of minigames and secure victory by winning the coveted neon Party Crown. Whether it is Hot Potato, Spike Attack, or Milky Way Moovers, you will have hours of fun - and chaos - in this multiplayer experience.

PartyVersus is available for $9.99 USD on the Meta Horizon Store or free for a limited time with a subscription to Meta Quest+. 

Play Anywhere. Party Everywhere!

- - - -

🎮 Available now on the Meta Horizon Store
▸  https://partyversus.com/

- - - -

📣 Stay informed:
▸ Website:  https://schellgames.com/
▸ Discord: https://discord.gg/schellgames

#schellgames #partyversus
